metadata.name: Floral Gold 1/1
metadata.description:
A stable convergence to retro resurgence. American dream on the loose (or Andaluse), IRL. An ode to glamor, credentials established, style nostalgic, 1950s vintage americana. Bouffanted beauty clashes with East Coast polish. Demure floral lace tie bow, frilled papaya mesh mini length dress, electric hoops. 

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up, 2020, photograph of a beautiful young 24 year old female model wearing a short red lace dress, pink lipstick, cute green purses, crystal earrings and an orange bandana, walking down Manhattan in the 1990s, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 75, scale: 13.
